cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.PL

The paper deals with model checking probabilistic CTL properties of Markov decision processes with convex uncertainties, which falls under the category of formal methods and verification (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the operations of parallel composition for composing interval MDP components at run-time, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The paper also deals with probabilistic bisimulation, which is related to control systems (cs.SY) and programming languages (cs.PL).
